  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study is conducted in Asia. The aim of this observational study is to evaluate the weight
      change from baseline while using Levemir速 in subjects with type 2 diabetes mellitus under
      normal clinical practice conditions in India.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
